Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:45.58,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:161703,165582}Doctor, please wait.\NPlease give her time until 12 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.58,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:165582,167584}– Please!\N– Please, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:52.54,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:170045,172547}No.\NWe can not wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:172547,175342}Kozue, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:175342,176385}Forgive me…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:13.19,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:190691,193193}Ayuhara Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.19,0:03:14.77,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:193193,194778}Don't you dare dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.13,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:214965,216133}Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.30,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:216133,218301}Captain…\NAyuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:43.26,Default,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:218301,223265}The Mighty Six\Nkeep their promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:44.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:223265,224182}Maya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:05.45,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:244286,245454}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.66,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:248373,249666}She doesn't need\Namputation anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:11.87,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:249666,251877}– Wonderful!\N– Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:15.88,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:253170,255881}But we have to watch\Nher condition for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.63,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:255881,258633}Now it all depends\Non her resilience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.59,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:258633,260594}No problem.\NNo problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.09,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:260594,263096}When it comes to resilience,\Nno one can beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.39,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:263096,265390}Kozue was through so much\Nand always pulled through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.64,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:265390,268643}That's right.\NCaptain is as tough as steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.64,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:268643,270645}It seems like a miracle\Nhappened in this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.36,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:278445,280363}We have to thank Maya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:41.61,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:280363,281615}I can't see her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:13.35,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:310477,313355}She is really healthy.\NI guess she owes it to volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.23,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:313355,315232}There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.65,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:315232,317651}– Thank goodness.\N– That's great to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.61,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:318652,320612}Kozue.\NKozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.53,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:320612,321530}Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:23.03,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:321530,323031}Shh!\NKeep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:323031,324407}Miss…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:325700,328078}She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:33.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:328078,333708}Kozue… I worried so much.\NYou look so pale…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.71,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:340966,343718}We are really relieved that things\Nare getting better here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:47.30,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:343718,347305}We owe it to Doctor Noma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.05,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:347305,350058}Pleased to meet you.\NMy name is Noma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.01,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:350058,352018}Pleasure is all mine.\NMy name is Ayuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:54.43,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:352018,354437}We are really thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:58.60,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:354437,358608}Oh no, there is no need.\NI only happened to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.65,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:358608,361653}But I have to say\Nshe took it really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:08.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:365615,368702}I am very happy that her\Nparents have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.32,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:368702,370328}Yes, they got here very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:14.20,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:370328,374207}Fortunately she got\Na bit better by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.87,Default,Ishida,0,0,0,,{TIME:374207,377878}I'm to blame for everything.\NAfter all, it was all my idea…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.92,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:377878,379921}Don't blame yourself.\NIt's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.54,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:379921,382549}Do you think worrying is what\NCaptain would have wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:27.76,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:383758,387762}I heard that there is a risk of developing\Na pneumonia after getting infected with tetanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.01,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:387762,390015}She will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.81,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:390015,393810}The fever came down\Nand I gave her antibiotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:38.31,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:393810,398315}I see. She had certain heart condition\Nwhen she started middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.64,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:398315,399649}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.48,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:399649,401484}You don't say?\NI would never have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:43.82,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:401484,403820}She is a picture of health now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.78,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:403820,406781}You don't see it very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:50.61,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:407657,410619}What about her leg?\NWill she be able to play again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.95,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:410619,411953}There is no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.16,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:411953,415165}It would be a different story if she\Nhad taken the antitoxin even an hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:57.20,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:415165,417208}But now,\Nshe is going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:59.21,Default,Doctor,0,0,0,,{TIME:417208,419210}Truly, it was a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:04.84,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:423423,424841}It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.67,Default,Takeichi,0,0,0,,{TIME:424841,426676}It's like yesterday\Nwas a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:19.56,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:438063,439564}Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:23.52,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:441983,443526}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:25.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:443526,445445}Oh, it's so bright…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.73,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:445445,447739}Kozue, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:30.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:449532,450367}Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:33.20,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:450367,453203}Kozue, Papa and Midori\Nare all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:456539,458249}W-What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.29,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:459709,462295}You're finally awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:45.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:462295,465924}Midori? Girls?\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.75,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:465924,467759}You got tetanus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:468802,470136}Tetanus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.51,Default,Makimura,0,0,0,,{TIME:470136,473515}Yes. Your wound from our match\Nagainst the Mighty Six got infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:473515,474808}W-What happened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.72,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:476393,477727}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.27,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:478895,480271}What matters is\Nthat you're alive now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:480271,481189}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.48,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:481189,482482}Everyone here saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:06.40,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:482482,486403}They even drove all the way to the university\Nhospital in the storm to get you the antitoxin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:486403,488697}Wow…\NYou did…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:11.57,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:488697,491574}No. It was Maya-san\Nand the Mighty Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:492242,494369}Mighty Six…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:502002,503586}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:504379,506631}A terrible storm broke out yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:506631,508633}The road has been blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:509676,512387}The contact with\Nthe outside world has been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:36.14,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:512387,516141}We had to get the antitoxin\Nfrom the university medical hospital in Ōsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:516141,519185}But an ambulance\Nwould have never made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.18,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:519185,521187}So Maya-san and her group\Ntried the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.85,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:523690,525859}Very well.\NLet's race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:50.23,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:525859,530238}I don't think I'll ever have the opportunity\Nto race to save someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.44,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:530238,531448}Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.95,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:533867,536953}They took that challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.95,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:536953,540957}Then they delivered the antitoxin\Nbefore 12 o'clock like they promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.87,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:540957,543877}Your life was saved.\NMaya-san won the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:13.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:549591,553053}I… I didn't know\NMaya-san was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:16.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:553053,556765}Where is she now?\NLet me talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.31,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:556765,560310}She's not here anymore.\NShe came here by herself, then she disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:21.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:560310,561728}By herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:24.60,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:561728,564606}What about the others?\NWhat happened to the Mighty Six's members?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:572781,574491}Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:36.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:575325,576785}Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:576785,578078}Forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:578078,578995}Ishimatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:47.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:586169,587420}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:592425,594052}Did she say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:594844,596638}Did she just disappear without a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.64,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:598306,599641}She said one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.06,Default,Inomata,0,0,0,,{TIME:599641,602060}That if we don't save you,\Nshe won't ever forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.94,Alternative,Maya,0,0,0,,{TIME:604604,606940}If you don't save her,\NI won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:609859,612362}Maya-san…\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:612362,615031}You put your life on the line\Nin order to save mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:615031,616991}Girls, let's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:616991,619494}I want to finally see\Nthe ball fly again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:619494,621079}I'm fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:24.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:621079,624124}Don't you want to feel again\Nwhat's it's like to receive, to spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:624124,626084}Why are we still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.72,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:643226,644727}Looks like she's fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.68,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:644727,646688}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.40,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,{TIME:647814,650400}But it's amazing how much strength\Nand energy those kids have—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.56,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:650400,651568}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:655822,657365}I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:657365,659159}I'm so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:03.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:659909,663788}Maya-san… I want to play volleyball\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:07.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:663788,667083}My love belongs\Nto the volleyball field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:667083,668918}Just like yours\Nbelongs to the motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:13.88,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:668918,673882}Maya-san, thanks to you,\NI've learned a lot in the last few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:673882,676259}I won't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:22.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:676259,682015}I will live my youth looking up,\Nchallenging the world…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:682015,683975}…just like you do every day.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:29.31,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:689314,689314}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.61,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:696321,697614}Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.03,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:697614,701034}It's been only a week, at least put on\Na hat to protect yourself from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:701034,703119}I'm not a kid anymore.\NI'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.41,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:703119,705413}By the way,\NI have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.16,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:705413,707165}Here, it's a letter from Midori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:708708,710126}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:710126,712212}Alright, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.42,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:712212,713420}Please don't go far.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.46,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:713420,714464}Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:58.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:716549,718635}I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.59,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:718635,720595}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:729854,732565}Ahh, it feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.65,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:732565,734651}Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:18.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:734651,738613}That's so like Midori. Everything's so pretty,\Nfrom the handwriting to the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:738613,740323}Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:740323,743785}"My dad told me that you are\Nrecovering slowly but steadily."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.28,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:743785,746287}"We're overjoyed\Nthat you're still here with us."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:29.79,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:746287,749791}Professor Hongou was visibly relieved when\Nwe told him and told me to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:34.17,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:749791,754170}We exercise every day\Nfor the next tournament until dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.56,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:771396,773564}We're a bit rusty after the holiday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:56.90,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:773564,776901}But the training is already showing results\Nand we start to regain our form.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:02.07,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:776901,782073}We all, Professor Hongou and us,\Ngreatly desire that we will win again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:783032,784742}"…that we will win again."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.95,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:784742,788955}"Please be patient and take\Nyour time to recover, Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:788955,790790}They're doing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:14.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:790790,794502}And here I am,\Njust sitting around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:16.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:794502,796921}I feel like I was left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:33.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:811728,813771}What a sorrowful whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:817650,819193}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.16,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:828745,830163}Oh! Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:830997,832665}"Yuuko"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:00.38,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:839547,840381}Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:13.10,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:851267,853102}Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:15.48,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:854520,855480}You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:856647,858441}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.40,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:859317,861402}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:24.94,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:861402,864947}Sorry I freaked you out\Nback there. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:869369,872080}What a strange,\Nyet familiar feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:36.16,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:872080,876167}My heart never pounded like this,\Nno matter how strong opponents I faced…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.54,Alternative,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:880546,882548}She's like her twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.42,Alternative,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:882548,884425}To think she's just\Na random stranger…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:48.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:885093,888971}He seemed to mistake me\Nfor someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:888971,890973}He clearly called me "Yuuko"…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:58.81,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:895144,898815}Kozue, you look flushed.\NDid your fever go up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:898815,900024}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:900024,902693}I just walked a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.23,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:902693,904237}I told you not to\Noverexert yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:06.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:904237,906614}I'm really okay, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:906614,908199}Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:10.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:908199,910535}But really,\Nlook at that wondrous sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:910535,914038}I didn't know the air in the mountains\Nwas so clear and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:914038,916207}Oh, great mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.45,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:916207,917458}Kozue?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.46,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:917458,919460}Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.29,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:919460,921295}Kozue, did something\Ngood happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:921295,923131}What makes you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.88,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:924298,925883}You look really cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.92,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:925883,928928}Well, it's no wonder.\NI'm able to walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.22,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:928928,930221}You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:930221,932557}Oh, it's him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:33.76,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:932557,933766}"Him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:933766,936060}Yes, it's someone I met during walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:936060,937979}Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.69,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:941816,944694}He looks really handsome.\NMaybe a university student?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:46.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:944694,946737}Him? Handsome where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:49.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:946737,949740}He was rude to me.\NHe mistook me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.70,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:950575,952702}Kozue, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:954036,955663}For real, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:957123,958749}I'm 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:03.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:958749,963004}Come on, Mama, how could you\Nforget your own daughter's age?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:05.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:963004,965131}But why are you asking me that\Nall of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.63,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:965131,966632}Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.59,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:966632,969594}We'd better get ready for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:972597,974390}Mom's being weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:974390,975892}"Kozue, how old are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:16.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:975892,976809}"17."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:976809,978978}"Yes! The best age there is."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:978978,982315}17 years old Kozue.\NAdolescence feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:985693,987195}Wait, did I fall in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:28.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:987195,988321}No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:35.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:991449,995536}When I transferred to Fujimi Academy\Nand met Tsutomu-kun for the first time…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:38.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:995536,998289}My heart was racing, too.\NBut it feels different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003085,1005046}When I looked at him…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005046,1007965}It was almost hypnotizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007965,1009467}It was hard to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010801,1013596}It was such an exciting sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:57.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013596,1017433}But I don't understand\Nthis strange feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:15.61,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033449,1035618}Huh? Tetanus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:17.57,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035618,1037578}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.74,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037578,1039747}It was a terrible storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:24.37,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041457,1044377}She needed immediate treatment,\Nand was about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.13,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045461,1048130}No car could make it.\NNot even helicopters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.84,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048130,1049840}Then how did she survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:33.67,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050716,1053678}She got the antitoxin from\Nthe nearby medical university hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.22,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053678,1056222}It was delivered by some bikers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.51,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056222,1057515}Bikers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:43.72,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060184,1063729}I heard about some bikers causing chaos in\Nthe mountains. I wonder if it were them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.40,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064981,1068401}By the way, I heard\Nthat he comes from Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.44,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068401,1070444}He's a second-year\Nuniversity student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070444,1072029}I can't believe you, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072029,1073698}How could you ask him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.69,0:17:55.95,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073698,1075950}I only happened to overhear\Nsome gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:59.32,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075950,1079328}You wouldn't have the courage\Nto ask him anyway, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079328,1080788}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082915,1085710}So, what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.71,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085710,1087712}You should ask him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088921,1091215}I don't care enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:14.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092258,1094093}But what did he come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.51,Default,Ayuhara's mom,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094093,1096512}If I had to guess,\NI'd say maybe hiking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097805,1099599}Hiking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.60,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099599,1101601}I wonder if that's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:31.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105771,1111027}When he called me Yuuko,\Nhe paled as if he saw a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.44,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111027,1113446}Maybe it meant\Nsomething traumatic for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.83,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121245,1123831}Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:53.96,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130171,1133966}He went down early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.09,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133966,1136093}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:59.38,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136093,1139388}Yes, and then he told me that\Nhe found something interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:02.64,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139388,1142642}…on the way to the mountains.\NSome broken motorcycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142642,1144644}Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145853,1147855}Where did he see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.69,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147855,1149690}How do I get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:11.94,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149690,1151942}First you have to cross a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.27,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151942,1154278}Then you pass a lumberjack hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154278,1155988}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.82,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155988,1157823}Hey! You can't push yourself yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.66,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157823,1160660}That way is too dangerous for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:31.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167917,1171045}I knew something bad\Nhappened to Maya-san's group.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171045,1172672}I need to check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:44.14,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179512,1184141}Excuse me, mister. Did you see\Na young man pass through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187520,1189230}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.73,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189230,1190731}Hey, wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.94,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193484,1194944}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:55.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194944,1195736}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199949,1202243}What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:03.99,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202243,1203994}It's a sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:11.00,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205037,1211001}Three years ago,\Na girl lost her life on this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.62,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211001,1213629}That girl…\Nwas Yuuko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.71,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213629,1215715}Yes, I believe that was her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.17,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215715,1219176}They went for a walk and wanted\Nto take a photo there…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:23.05,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219176,1223055}…when the rock suddenly\Ncollapsed under her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.64,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223055,1225641}It was a terrible sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:28.68,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225641,1228686}She was such a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:32.48,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228686,1232481}The boy comes to visit her grave\Nevery year ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.10,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232481,1235109}He always puts\Nsuch beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:40.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238195,1240156}I have dark memories\Nof my own, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.78,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240156,1241782}Tsutomu-kun's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.61,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241782,1244618}Even now, I feel it\Nengraved deep into my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.70,Default,Grandpa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247663,1249707}Really, she looks just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:55.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251375,1255588}Yuuko-san has died in these\Nmountains whereas I lived on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:59.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255588,1259675}One life was taken away,\Nand one life continues on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.09,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263262,1264096}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.14,Alternative,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270978,1272146}What was she doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.73,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276984,1278736}What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278736,1280780}I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.40,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283491,1285409}Were you trying to kill yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.53,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285409,1287536}You should be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.70,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287536,1289705}Your life was just saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:33.12,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289705,1293125}Do you remember how much everyone\Nstruggled so that you could survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.54,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293125,1294543}Or did you forget that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:38.08,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297254,1298088}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:41.88,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300966,1301884}Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301884,1302968}B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.55,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302968,1304553}It's not the time to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.30,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304553,1306305}Don't you care\Nwhat happens to your leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:48.39,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306305,1308390}Are you fine if you\Ncan't play volleyball anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:01.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320402,1321237}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.86,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321237,1323864}Wow, you weigh more\Nthan I thought, chubby girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.82,0:22:07.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324824,1327326}Hey, I'm not chubby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.32,0:22:09.41,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328327,1329411}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329411,1330746}Ayuhara Kozue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:15.25,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332331,1335251}Well, that name isn't so bad that you\Nhad to jump into water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335251,1337378}Stop making fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337378,1338754}Let me get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.75,0:22:20.13,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338754,1340130}I'm sorry,\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.92,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340130,1341924}I'm Yushima Jirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:25.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343384,1345553}U-Uhm…\NPlease let me get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:26.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345553,1346679}It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.76,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346679,1347763}I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.76,0:22:28.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347763,1348806}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:35.27,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353269,1355271}You startled me\Nwhen we met for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.27,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355271,1357273}I thought you were\Na ghost of my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.02,0:22:40.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358023,1360025}Little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.60,0:22:42.86,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360609,1362862}Yes, remember how\NI called you Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.86,0:22:45.07,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1362862,1365072}It's the name of my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.07,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365072,1367074}If you're not careful,\Nyou'll end up like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369410,1372955}You're right, but I wanted to see the crashed\Nmotorbikes that I was told you found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:56.37,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1372955,1376375}Crashed motorbikes\Nare not people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:57.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376375,1377751}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.67,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1378294,1380671}– Miss!\N– Kozue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:03.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382214,1383799}Oh! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:07.63,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1385509,1387636}Alright, from here\Nyou better go on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:09.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388220,1389138}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:12.97,Default,Yushima,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389138,1392975}Be careful and take\Ngood care of your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:17.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394768,1397021}You can bet I will heal soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397021,1399023}I don't want to waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:22.02,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1399023,1402026}I will walk by myself,\Nwith all I have like I always did.
Comment: 0,0:23:56.43,0:23:56.43,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1436435,1436435}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:03.40,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439355,1443400}The Fujimi team travels to Nagano\Nto train for the next Interhigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:08.53,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443400,1448530}There, Kozue once again hears\Nthe beautiful melodic whistle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.53,0:24:10.90,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448530,1450908}She meets Yushima again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:14.45,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450908,1454453}In the meantime Fujimi\Nis challenged by Aoba Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:20.58,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454453,1460584}Kozue gets to see Yamamoto's eerie figure on\Nthe court again, along with someone unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.58,0:24:24.08,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460584,1464088}Please look forward to the next episode.
